<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>cocopos - ÂøÉ„ÅÆ„Éù„Çπ„Éà</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
